17-03-14T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"其實依隻遊戲比較難入門，個系統好複雜....<br />\n新手一開始應該點做，諗緊買唔買"},{"pid":"29e063d7900aea8d4dd7e59a4bbfec419666cfc5","tid":151410,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"點用海軍運軍去第二度？"},{"pid":"867b4421bc9b9be4f6bbe8f0b6159ce579058ec3","tid":151410,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點用海軍運軍去第二度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果是目的地由盟國控制or取得到該國軍事進出的權利, 把部隊調動至出發地海港,點選部隊跟著右擊目的地海港<br />\n<br />\n若是登陸敵國控制之地區, 則需在battle plan中下達命令, 不過此需確保海域的制海和制空權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b32ec48466b6424df9c11547a65132d9627731","tid":151410,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實依隻遊戲比較難入門，個系統好複雜....<br />\n新手一開始應該點做，諗緊買唔買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為4相比1-3集已經簡化了很多<br />\n<br />\n新手選擇強國, 如德國會比較容易"},{"pid":"9d9b66f7f1c351332e430b2493ca8dddeb5524a7","tid":151410,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實依隻遊戲比較難入門，個系統好複雜....<br />\n新手一開始應該點做，諗緊買唔買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為4相比1-3集已經簡化了很多<br />\n<br />\n新手選擇強國, 如德國會比較容易</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要是建軍和出兵打仗<br />\n<br />\n其他如外交,建設(道路, 防禦工事, 兵工廠, oil plant和核反應堆 etc.), 內政, 貿易, 科研和軍備製造"},{"pid":"274c02d4fa3d81c05b522ffa8efcbfa8c8dd92e1","tid":151410,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c264385e1c2d8e5f00ae83318ea3e46c858f6699","tid":151410,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"我想有 East VS West<br />\n再整個HONG KONG MOD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最後計劃腰斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm